If you're expecting something in the style of Fast & Furious, guess again. Obscene cars isn't enough, there has to be some actual acting involved, otherwise you'd be as well watching a few episodes of Top Gear. This can not be levelled at Gone in 60 seconds, it excells in all areas, reminiscent of Mr McQueen's automobile orientated productions. A careful piece of direction blends the brat pack in with the old school, in what will undoubtedly make an appealing choice for most viewers. 

IMHO rating : 80%
